# Upstream inkle/inky uses Git LFS for the inklecate compiler binaries.
# This fork was created from the GitHub source ZIP, which contains only
# the *LFS pointer files* (~130 bytes each), not the real binaries.
# To keep this repository cloneable without LFS configured we therefore
# do NOT re-enable LFS here. The pointer files are committed as plain
# text and the original LFS rules are kept here only as a historical
# reference:
#
#     app/main-process/ink/inklecate_* filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
#     app/main-process/ink/inkjs-compatible/inklecate_* filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
#
# To actually run or package this fork you need the real inklecate
# binaries. Get them from an official Inky release at
# https://github.com/inkle/inky/releases  (download the matching OS
# build and copy the inklecate_* files into the matching paths above)
# or clone the upstream repository with `git lfs install` enabled.
